snippet.title: The Bornless | Pre-Alpha Gameplay Teaser #1
snippet.description:
The Bornless is a multiplayer horror game currently under development, close to a playable alpha.
https://www.thebornless.com/
 
The Bornless NFTs are made up of 8 collections, each representing one of the 8 characters in the game's story, each collection containing 666 items.

Each NFT grants the owner access to one of the tournaments within The Bornless game. There shall be 8 tournaments, one for each collection, which will be held after a stable release of the game. Anybody can be nominated to play on behalf of the NFT owner.

The winner of the tournament will receive the final item, number 666 in that collection, and a great secret will be revealed to them.
